Time Series Object Oriented (OO) Vignette
==========================================

Description:
    Implements an Object Oriented TimeSeries class encapsulating a full
    time series analysis and forecasting pipeline. Generates synthetic
    data (sinusoidal + trend + white noise), then applies the class methods
    for visualization, statistical testing, decomposition, and ARIMA
    forecasting.

    TimeSeries class methods:
        - __init__()            Instantiate with ts and optional train_size
        - lineplot()            Plot the time series
        - plot_hist_qq()        Histogram and Q-Q plot for normality check
        - acf_pacf_plots()      ACF and PACF plots
        - test_ADF_stationary() Augmented Dickey-Fuller stationarity test
        - decompose()           STL decomposition into trend/seasonal/residual
        - arima()               Fit ARIMA model with given order
        - auto_arima()          Auto-select best ARIMA via pmdarima BIC
        - test_markov_regime()  Markov Regime switching model
        - get_train_test()      Return train/test split
        - predict()             Forecast with auto_arima on test set
        - predict_plot()        Plot forecasts vs actuals with confidence interval

Data:
    Synthetic: sinusoidal + linear trend + Gaussian white noise
    (pd.date_range 2000-2020, monthly frequency)

References:
    1. statsmodels time series
       https://www.statsmodels.org
    2. pmdarima auto_arima
       http://alkaline-ml.com/pmdarima
    3. ADF stationarity test
       https://www.statsmodels.org/dev/generated/statsmodels.tsa.stattools.adfuller.html

